      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag Type D 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, paired with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe for total mechanical peace of mind. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with original bushings and a perfectly calibrated M-Variable Differential Lock. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, this unit showcases a pristine undercarriage and a cabin free of typical bolster wear or pixel degradation. A definitive example of analog performance engineering.",
