      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time-capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every switch, button, and digital interface operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in absolute peak condition. Includes all original keys, window sticker, and factory manuals.",
